<div id="newsletter-popup" class="popup-overlay">
  <div id="popup-content-wrapper" class="popup-content">
    <div class="popup-image">
      <img src="/full-inbox.jpg" alt="An overflowing email inbox" />
    </div>
    <div class="popup-text-content">
      <button id="popup-close" class="close-button">&times;</button>
      <h2>Sign up for my newsletter!</h2>
      <p>You have visited my personal website, which strongly indicates you would like very frequent updates from me piling up in your inbox. Choose which option works best for you:</p>
 
      <div class="popup-options">
        <div class="popup-option">
          <h3>Daily Updates</h3>
          <p>I'm dying to hear about what you had for breakfast.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="popup-option">
          <h3>Hourly Updates</h3>
          <p>My inbox has an unquenchable thirst for Oliver's opinions, profound witticisms, and carefully curated sponsored content.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="popup-option">
          <h3>More, More, More</h3>
          <p>Please just email me constantly. I don't care about what. AI-generated content? Yes, please. Just keep it coming.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<style>
  .popup-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 1010;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
  }
 
  .popup-overlay.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
 
  .popup-content {
    display: flex;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    max-width: 750px;
    width: 90%;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transform: scale(0.95);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
 
  .popup-image {
    flex-basis: 35%;
    display: flex;
    overflow: hidden;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .popup-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
 
  .popup-text-content {
    position: relative;
    flex-basis: 60%;
    padding: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #333;
  }
 
  .popup-overlay.visible .popup-content {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
 
  .popup-content h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #111;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
 
  .popup-content > p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
 
  .close-button {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #999;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
 
  .close-button:hover {
    color: #333;
  }
 
  .popup-options {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
 
  .popup-option {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
    text-align: left;
  }
 
  .popup-option:hover {
    border-color: #999;
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
  }
 
  .popup-option h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
 
  .popup-option p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
 
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .popup-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 370px;
      margin-left: 0;
      width: 90%;
    }
 
    .popup-image {
      flex-basis: 100px;
      width: 100%;
    }
 
    .popup-text-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .popup-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .popup-content > p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .popup-option {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .popup-option h3 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .popup-option p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>